OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FGenerally
OL,6,Fdry conditions across the region with
OL,7,Fpartly cloudy skies. Winds will ease
OL,8,Fto become light for most but still
OL,9,Fbreezier across Norfolk and along the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FGenerally dry with bright
OL,13,Fspells, although rather cloudier at
OL,14,Ftimes. Some longer sunny spells likely
OL,15,Fto develop later in the day. Light
OL,16,Fwinds inland, a little breezier along
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
